title: Lukas Graham Enlisted Kelsea Ballerini For a Gorgeous Version of "7 Years"
text:
Kelsea Ballerini Performance Video at the 2017 Grammys Lukas Graham Enlisted Kelsea Ballerini For a Gorgeous Version of "7 Years" February 12, 2017 by Maggie Pehanick 102 Shares 
If you've heard "7 Years" on the radio a million times and you're still not sick of it, then this performance is for you. Country up-and-comer Kelsea Ballerini joined Lukas Graham for a performance of his hit at the Grammys, and it's just plain gorgeous. Listen above!
